<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="e0a0gz" data-video-descrip="The &amp;quot;The Legends of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel&amp;quot; games certainly have no shortage (get it?) of jokes when it comes to the stature of Towa Herschel, one of the game's smallest cast members despite being 21 years of age. Upon arrival at the town that is the base of his new workplace, Leeves, Rean Schwarzer is brought up short (see what I did there?) by the arrival of Towa." data-video-title="Did You Not Recognize Me?" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/e0a0gz_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/did_you_not_recognize_me.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/DownHereShot" data-video-tropename="&quot;Down Here!&quot; Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="2" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/TheLegendOfHeroesTrailsOfColdSteel" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Did You Not Recognize Me?</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The &quot;The Legends of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel&quot; games certainly have no shortage (get it?) of jokes when it comes to the stature of Towa Herschel, one of the game's smallest cast members despite being 21 years of age. Upon arrival at the town that is the base of his new workplace, Leeves, Rean Schwarzer is brought up short (see what I did there?) by the arrival of Towa. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
